{"tid":2255241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國義士獲釋即獄前示威：總理下台，否則升高抗爭！","createTime":"2020-10-23T11:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T00:54:54.000Z","uid":337052,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6b14f405feb93bb449fa9842080aef02c1da808c","tid":2255241,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"集會頭領獲釋後當即豎三指：總理不下台將提升集會等級<br />\n2020年10月23日 - by hushjoker<br />\nSHARETWEETSHARE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ElAUHKbVkAAOquT-735x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FElAUHKbVkAAOquT-735x400.jpg&h=0f1bd204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國頭條新聞社訊據泰媒報導10月23日當地時間16：44於曼谷特別監獄，<span class=\"red\">此前於13日被警方逮捕的集會頭領&ldquo;湃道丁&rdquo;被保釋出獄，許多民眾前來為其加油打氣。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">湃道丁被釋放後便走上集會民眾在監獄前設置的演講台，手豎三指表示出獄後的首件事情便是趕巴育總理下台。隨後在第二次上台演講時稱，如果巴育總理不在明天之內辭職，將提高集會等級，並要求釋放還在獄中關押的7名集會頭領及集會人員。</span><br />\n<br />\n據悉，今晨法院通過對湃道丁的保釋決定，因其仍是學生身份，且在獄中表現良好、無越獄及製造事端的跡象，法院同意以7萬泰銖的保釋金對其進行保釋。隨後，遠進黨議員本雅乍以議員身份做擔保代替現金保釋。 （編譯：hush 來源：ThaiPBS)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ElAeFWlUwAItOuj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FElAeFWlUwAItOuj.jpg&h=492a3c9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ElAeg8vVkAARnpX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FElAeg8vVkAARnpX.jpg&h=44325fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e5%a4%b4%e9%a2%86%e8%8e%b7%e9%87%8a%e5%90%8e%e5%bd%93%e5%8d%b3%e7%ab%96%e4%b8%89%e6%8c%87%ef%bc%9a%e6%80%bb%e7%90%86%e4%b8%8d%e4%b8%8b%e5%8f%b0%e5%b0%86%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e9%9b%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c