,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">集會組織公佈23日集會地點</span></strong><br />\n2020年10月23日 - by hushjoker<br />\nSHARETWEETSHARE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20201023172354-735x400.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE_20201023172354-735x400.png&h=d462d654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國頭條新聞社訊 <span class=\"red\">據泰媒報導 10月23日，集會組織&ldquo;解放青年&rdquo;在其主頁發文公佈今日集會地點：</span><br />\n1.曼谷地區<br />\n15：00 HuaMak警察署前方<br />\n16：00 曼谷特別監獄前方<br />\n17：00 The Mall Bangkapi商場前方<br />\n2.北部地區<br />\n17：00 清邁府Thungphabod PPT加油站前方<br />\n16：00 南奔府Mahawong寺前方<br />\n3.中部地區<br />\n17：00 北欖坡府政府前方<br />\n4.東北部地區<br />\n17：00 孔敬府Ratchada Nuson公園<br />\n（編譯：hush 來源：Springnews）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20201023172044-1080x1080.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE_20201023172044-1080x1080.png&h=192dfd8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e7%bb%84%e7%bb%87%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%8323%e6%97%a5%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e5%9c%b0%e7%82%b9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2F%25e9%259b%2586%25e4%25bc%259a%25e7%25bb%2584%25e7%25bb%2587%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%25b8%258323%25e6%2597%25a5%25e9%259b%2586%25e4%25bc%259a%25e5%259c%25b0%25e7%2582%25b9%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=48a9df87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e7%bb%84%e7%bb%87%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%8323%e6%97%a5%e9%9b%86%e4%bc%9a%e5%9